MULTAN, Jul 26 (APP):Foreign Minister Makhdoom Shah Mahmood Hussain Qureshi here Monday expressed grief and sorrow over death of elder brother of Provincial Minister for Energy Dr Akhtar Malik, Haji Ata Muhammad.
In condolence message, the foreign minister prayed to Allah Almighty to rest the departed soul in eternal peace and grant courage to members the bereaved family to bear this irreparable loss with fortitude.
